1
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:26,990
[Brocade Odyssey]

2
00:01:27,210 --> 00:01:29,810
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:31,270 --> 00:01:33,360
The land of Shu always regards red silk as precious.

4
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:36,550
Mr. Ji's Shu Red Silk is even more renowned.

5
00:01:36,950 --> 00:01:38,680
Ms. Ji, you dyed a lot of silks.

6
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:39,870
Why aren't any silks dyed red?

7
00:01:40,270 --> 00:01:42,160
I'll dye any color I want.

8
00:01:42,510 --> 00:01:44,550
Mr. Yang, it's none of your concern.

9
00:01:46,630 --> 00:01:47,760
That's the main gate.

10
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:49,160
Please.

11
00:01:50,440 --> 00:01:53,160
We have quite a number of guests today.

12
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,830
What is she doing here?

13
00:01:58,830 --> 00:02:00,230
I don't know, either.

14
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:04,160
Yingying, come and greet Mrs. Zhao now.

15
00:02:07,830 --> 00:02:08,670
Good morrow, Mrs. Zhao.

16
00:02:10,910 --> 00:02:13,470
Although your family is not a noble household,

17
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,000
there's no reason for your daughter

18
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,630
to be running around every day.

19
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:19,720
It's one thing when she spends all her time outside.

20
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,960
However, she even brings men to the house.

21
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,080
It's a minor matter

22
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:26,630
if Ms. Ji's reputation is tarnished when this spreads,

23
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,630
but what of your family's honor?

24
00:02:32,270 --> 00:02:33,190
You misunderstood me.

25
00:02:33,470 --> 00:02:35,270
He's here to meet Yaoting for business.

26
00:02:35,270 --> 00:02:36,720
I just happened to chance upon him.

27
00:02:36,910 --> 00:02:37,470
Yes.

28
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,600
It's just a friendly reminder.

29
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,670
Pay no mind to me

30
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:43,830
if you think it is no trouble.

31
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:46,030
I fear that should something disgraceful

32
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,670
happen one day,

33
00:02:49,110 --> 00:02:52,270
it will be too late for regrets by then.

34
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,670
You're right, Mrs. Zhao.

35
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,880
Even a misunderstanding

36
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:01,630
could make those who are clueless tattle.

37
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,030
I'll make sure to discipline her so as to avert

38
00:03:04,270 --> 00:03:05,630
even the smallest mistake.

39
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,080
However, I believe

40
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,960
a sharp person like you

41
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,520
would not misunderstand.

42
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,080
Come, Mrs. Zhao. This way.

43
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,390
It turns out that even you

44
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:25,320
have moments of meekness and grace.

45
00:03:26,270 --> 00:03:27,270
You have visited my home.

46
00:03:27,270 --> 00:03:28,960
I have kept my end of the bargain.

47
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,320
You can get your drink from another house now.

48
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:37,910
Mrs. Ji, I will take my leave now.

49
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,600
Ting.

50
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,320
Stop right there!

51
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:00,670
Mother, I'm wrong.

52
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,630
Mother, stay away!

53
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:04,080
- Mother! - Ji Yingying!

54
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,000
Get here now.

55
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:06,000
Ji Yingying.

56
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:06,390
Mother!

57
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:06,670
Ji Yingying.

58
00:04:06,670 --> 00:04:07,670
Don't hit me!

59
00:04:07,670 --> 00:04:08,240
Ji Yingying.

60
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:08,520
Don't...!

61
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,550
Get here now!

62
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,550
- Mother! - Who was that man?

63
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:13,960
Mother...

64
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:16,270
That was Mr. Yang.

65
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:19,110
He's doing business with our family.

66
00:04:19,110 --> 00:04:19,790
Business?

67
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,480
Is that true?

68
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,320
Do you think you can fool me

69
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,230
just because I'm no longer in charge?

70
00:04:26,110 --> 00:04:27,510
His clothing alone made it clear

71
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,070
that he is no ordinary folk.

72
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,040
Why would he do business with us?

73
00:04:32,510 --> 00:04:34,110
He came to inquire about Shu Red Silk.

74
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:35,670
Shu Red Silk?

75
00:04:37,350 --> 00:04:38,670
Shu Red Silk again?

76
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,950
It has been so many years.

77
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,270
These people won't stop.

78
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:50,440
[Notice]

79
00:04:57,790 --> 00:04:59,720
[Brocade Bureau]
You're here early.

80
00:05:00,790 --> 00:05:02,480
Did Chief Sang truly agree to post the notice

81
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,720
to stop the monopolization of the creek?

82
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:05,880
It's all thanks to me.

83
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,480
You should

84
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,320
have done it earlier.

85
00:05:11,550 --> 00:05:13,440
Is your father as unreliable

86
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,880
as you too?

87
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,230
My father is a dignified

88
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,720
and respected government officer

89
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,230
of the country.

90
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,600
You think he's unreliable?

91
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,350
What did you mean?

92
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:24,350
Did you just call me unreliable?

93
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:28,720
Listen. Show some respect to the honorary president.

94
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,160
Now listen to me.

95
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,510
If you succeed this time,

96
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:32,640
I'll give you a deep bow

97
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:34,110
every time

98
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,110
I see you.

99
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,040
Father!

100
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,760
Chief Sang.

101
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:42,720
Hurry up and put up the notice.

102
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,070
They...

103
00:05:43,070 --> 00:05:44,390
What trouble are you causing?

104
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,550
Go home now!

105
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:46,550
Chief Sang,

106
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,070
Huanhua Creek is in constant turmoil.

107
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,070
Do you have a solution?

108
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:52,720
This is no longer

109
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,550
under my control.

110
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:58,070
Not under your control?

111
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:00,510
Funnily enough,

112
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:03,480
I'm only temporarily filling the spot of a brocade officer.

113
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:06,160
The newly transferred brocade officer has arrived.

114
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,510
It has been over a month.

115
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,070
And yet, he is nowhere to be seen.

116
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:11,000
Perhaps he

117
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,160
is afraid to come.

118
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,640
All of you know Mr. Shen,

119
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:17,270
the previous brocade officer who died

120
00:06:17,270 --> 00:06:18,720
two years upon his arrival.

121
00:06:18,880 --> 00:06:22,110
Mr. Zhang, the one before him, fell off a horse and died.

122
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:23,760
The previous one...

123
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,830
Chief Sang,

124
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:28,720
we rely on this to make ends meet.

125
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:29,880
This is important.

126
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,670
Do you know who is in charge

127
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:33,000
of this matter now?

128
00:06:33,110 --> 00:06:33,880
Yes, Father.

129
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,040
Get to the point...!

130
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:35,670
Hold your tongue!

131
00:06:38,110 --> 00:06:38,950
Yesterday

132
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:42,440
was the deadline for the new brocade officer to take office.

133
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,320
We all thought he was not coming.

134
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:47,350
Who would have thought that the new brocade officer

135
00:06:47,350 --> 00:06:49,550
took office just as the deadline was about to pass?

136
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:51,480
Naturally, I stepped down.

137
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,480
From henceforth,

138
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,230
I will continue my duties,

139
00:06:54,230 --> 00:06:55,670
while the brocade officer will continue his.

140
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:56,880
You will have to look

141
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,270
for him for this matter.

142
00:06:58,670 --> 00:06:59,480
Why did he have

143
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,270
to take office

144
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:01,670
yesterday?

145
00:07:01,670 --> 00:07:02,480
Exactly.

146
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:06,640
What is the new brocade officer like?

147
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,390
You will know when you meet him.

148
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,670
A new brocade officer?

149
00:07:10,670 --> 00:07:11,950
Let me see who he is!

150
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,350
Let me see who he is!

151
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,040
Take him away!

152
00:07:14,110 --> 00:07:15,110
Open the door! Come out!

153
00:07:15,110 --> 00:07:15,760
Let me see you!

154
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,670
Hold your tongue!

155
00:07:18,070 --> 00:07:18,480
Stop him!

156
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:19,720
Don't worry, I got this.

157
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,760
Enough...

158
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:24,320
Chief Sang,

159
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:27,880
your attitude has changed.

160
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:30,040
I don't think it's just because of the new officer, right?

161
00:07:34,510 --> 00:07:36,070
This is the army's arrow.

162
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,880
Who have we crossed?

163
00:07:41,350 --> 00:07:42,640
This is more complex than it seems.

164
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:46,230
Act accordingly, Ms. Ji.

165
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,350
Yingying,

166
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:55,040
what do we do now?

167
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,670
We followed your words.

168
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:59,230
We have thought of ways to take orders from others

169
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:01,550
to prevent Mrs. Hua from driving us into destruction.

170
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:03,670
If we can't wash our silks

171
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:04,880
and deliver the goods on time,

172
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:07,880
we will lose a lot of money.

173
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:23,720
I, Ji Yingying, a humble servant seeks an audience with the new brocade officer!

174
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:25,640
It concerns life and death!

175
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:26,920
I humbly ask for permission!

176
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,320
I, Ji Yingying, a humble servant...

177
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,470
Seek an audience with the new brocade officer!

178
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:36,350
It concerns life and death!

179
00:08:36,430 --> 00:08:37,660
[Brocade Bureau]
We humbly ask for permission!

180
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,960
It concerns life and death!

181
00:08:40,670 --> 00:08:41,350
Mr. Yang,

182
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:43,150
while I am related to the Wang family by marriage,

183
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,880
our family is not involved in tax evasion.

184
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,350
You can check our accounts.

185
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,520
I'll speak...

186
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:52,150
The Li family had a spot

187
00:08:52,150 --> 00:08:53,150
at Huanhua Creek

188
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,640
as they persuaded others

189
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,200
with their influence.

190
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,110
Mr. Wang from Jinxiu Court

191
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:00,910
will fart in front of

192
00:09:00,910 --> 00:09:03,150
the opposite store on the first day of every month!

193
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:03,520
Mr...

194
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,550
Mr. Zhao Senior did not wash his feet for eight years

195
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,960
to be the Brocade Master!

196
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,150
Seeking for an audience!

197
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,030
It concerns life and death!

198
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,230
The people outside...?

199
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:16,280
No.

200
00:09:16,470 --> 00:09:17,790
Seeking for an audience!

201
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:18,400
I have

202
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,640
made up my mind not to see

203
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:21,150
anyone in the days to come.

204
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,440
Appearing at the most crucial moment

205
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,880
is how you leave a great impression.

206
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,640
Change to a new batch.

207
00:09:28,110 --> 00:09:29,440
Seeking for an audience!

208
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:31,400
It concerns life and death!

209
00:09:32,350 --> 00:09:32,960
That one

210
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,280
with a beard.

211
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:35,710
Yes.

212
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:39,080
It concerns life and death! I humbly ask for permission!

213
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:40,640
Stop it.

214
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:45,440
We have shouted for so long.

215
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,350
He won't open the door.

216
00:09:46,710 --> 00:09:48,670
He does not want to see us.

217
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,520
Do not fret.

218
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,080
Since all the orders

219
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,280
are from families with large dyeing business,

220
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,470
they must have places to wash silk.

221
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,350
I'll discuss with them

222
00:09:59,350 --> 00:10:01,080
and see if they can lend their place to us.

223
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,760
Mrs. Hua didn't come.

224
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:06,960
What do you mean?

225
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,520
Who is against us most

226
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:14,880
in this matter?

227
00:10:15,110 --> 00:10:16,080
Mrs. Hua.

228
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:17,440
She has not sent

229
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,350
a single servant to inquire us as of today.

230
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,840
What does that mean?

231
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:21,880
What does it mean?

232
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:22,760
Right. What does it mean?

233
00:10:23,470 --> 00:10:25,520
She already knows the outcome of today.

234
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,000
She has probably cut off

235
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,470
all our means of survival.

236
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:31,470
Is Mrs. Hua that impressive?

237
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:34,550
She didn't dominate Huanhua Creek for more than a decade

238
00:10:35,030 --> 00:10:36,910
by just being rude and overbearing.

239
00:10:37,670 --> 00:10:39,080
I have never underestimated her.

240
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,640
Yingying!

241
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,440
[Brocade Bureau]
Bad news!

242
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:43,910
Bad news!

243
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:44,840
Your family is in trouble!

244
00:10:53,710 --> 00:10:56,320
You have served many brocade officers.

245
00:10:57,470 --> 00:10:59,110
I know you're more familiar with the affairs

246
00:10:59,470 --> 00:11:00,590
of a brocade officer than me.

247
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:03,150
I hope you will continue to guide me.

248
00:11:04,110 --> 00:11:05,880
We will give you our loyalty

249
00:11:05,880 --> 00:11:07,880
and serve you with all our effort.

250
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,840
I don't need your loyalty.

251
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,320
However, if you dare to do what

252
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,880
I have forbidden,

253
00:11:18,350 --> 00:11:19,350
I can assure that

254
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,880
you will disappear before I do.

255
00:11:23,280 --> 00:11:23,880
Understand?

256
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:24,880
Understand.

257
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,230
I also do not wish anyone to know

258
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,440
about my position as the brocade officer yet.

259
00:11:29,520 --> 00:11:30,320
Yes!

260
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,960
As all of you know,

261
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:35,080
I'm a timid person,

262
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:37,520
and I'm afraid of death.

263
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:40,840
However, many of the brocade officers have died.

264
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:43,710
I believe all of you, who have served for many years,

265
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:46,320
know what the previous

266
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,520
brocade officers did.

267
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,960
Please write all of them

268
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:50,880
in great detail.

269
00:11:51,230 --> 00:11:52,110
I will consider it

270
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:54,280
a guide, too.

271
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:57,320
Mr. Yang, there is so much.

272
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,590
How can we write them all?

273
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:00,000
That's right.

274
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:02,030
Write up there.

275
00:12:02,150 --> 00:12:03,110
No... I'll write here.

276
00:12:03,110 --> 00:12:04,110
I'll write now.

277
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:04,760
I'll write.

278
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,880
Give me a paper!

279
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:09,470
Give me!

280
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,350
We only have one loom!

281
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:12,670
You can't take it!

282
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,760
You can't!

283
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:14,470
Stop!

284
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:15,230
Stop! You can't take it!

285
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,230
Put it down!

